'''Jimaguayú Municipal Museum''' is a [[museum]] located in [[Jimaguayú]], [[Cuba]]. It was established on 27 December 1982.<ref name="cult">{{cite web|url=http://www.cnpc.cult.cu/institucion/568 |title=Museo Municipal de Jimaguayú &#124; Portal del Consejo Nacional de Patrimonio Cultural |publisher=cnpc.cult.cu|accessdate=2015-11-01}}</ref>

The museum holds collections on history, weaponry and numismatics.

